dataList.name: PhotoGrid Lite: Photo Collage Maker & Photo Editor

dataList.appIntro:
Why you need PhotoGrid Lite?
With Instagram 1:1, 4:5 & 9:16 aspect ratio cropping. Brightness, contrast, saturation and huge adjustment. As well as text, blur, focus, mosaic, border, draw and watermark features. We really do have everything which you can share your photo on Tik Tok, Vigo video, Facebook...etc.
PhotoGrid team presents the compact PhotoGrid Lite photo editor! It's smaller in size but packs just as much power as its predecessor! Less storage and data are required, but all your favorite features still available, so you could enjoy a lag-free photo editing experience.
❤Highlights❤
☆ A must-have photo editor: Smaller in size, but packs more power.
☆ Small installation pack(13MB): Compact, fast download and low storage use.
☆ Less mobile data required: Edit/Grid your creations offline. No network required.
☆ Low storage & battery consumption: Designed for low-end mobile device users
❤Features❤
► Grid: Edit, grid or frame your photos in seconds!
► Beauty Camera: Taking selfie with our beauty camera. Real-time filter also
► Edit: Powerful editing tools to help your make stunning creations!
► Scrapbook: Create your own freestyle album that looks just like a real scrapbook
► Poster: Tons of stylish templates, beautify your creations without editing!
► Filmstrip: Create horizontal/vertical filmstrips, or make a sketch!
► Store: Various new stickers, backgrounds, filters updated every week.
❤Functions❤
• Grid: 300+ grid templates, that supports up to 15 images. 
• Scrapbook: Adjustable image size and location, grid up to 15 photos!
• Poster: 200+ poster templates, such as festive, PIP, magazines and more!
• Stickers: 500+ stickers, emoticons, flowers, beautify, cuties, you name it!
• Filters: 100+ filters, Greece blue, Paris pink, beautify, black & white etc.
• Backgrounds: 400+ backgrounds, deep space, animals, fruits, totem, rainbow and the list goes on.
• Edit: With Instagram 1:1, 4:5 & 9:16 aspect ratio cropping. Brightness, contrast, saturation and huge adjustment. As well as text, blur, focus, mosaic, border, draw and watermark features. We really do have everything. 
If you want to check out our other features, such as Video Collage, AR Face Filter, Slideshow, Pattern, Meme, GIF etc. Please download and install the full version of PhotoGrid: https://goo.gl/KRa4w3
